net.sourceforge.waters.model.base

Class AbstractHashCodeVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.waters.model.base.AbstractHashCodeVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ProxyVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModuleHashCodeVisitor, ProductDESHashCodeVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractHashCodeVisitor
extends Object
implements ProxyVisitor
    A visitor to compute hash code for Proxy objects based on their contents. It can be parameterised to respect or not to respect the geometry information for in some Proxy objects.
    Author:
    Robi Malik
    See Also:
    AbstractEqualityVisitor
